<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Maplayer.KR</title>

        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.0.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-cookie/1.4.1/jquery.cookie.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/4cdc6862b3.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="./script/script.js"></script>
        <script src="./script/register.js"></script>

        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style/style.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style/login.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <%- include("./Etc/header.ejs") %>
        <%- include("./Etc/errorModal.ejs") %>

        <div class="container randomBackground" id="randomBackground">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <p id="subTitle">회원가입</p>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <p id="title">Register</p>
            </div>

            <form method="POST" action="/register/register" onsubmit="return checkRegister()">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <input class="form-control" id="userName" name="userName" type="text" placeholder="아이디">
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <a>아이디는 이메일 형식으로만 가능합니다.</a>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <input class="form-control" id="passWord" name="passWord" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호">
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <a>비밀번호는 영어, 숫자와 특수문자를 포함한 8자리 이상이여야 합니다.</a>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <input class="form-control" id="passWordCheck" name="passWordCheck" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호 재입력">
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <input class="form-control" id="apiKey" name="apiKey" type="text" placeholder="API Key">
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <a>API Key 발급 방법　</a><a id="apiKeyRedirict" href="/apikey">[ 바로가기 ]</a>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-orange" id="checkApiKey" type="button">캐릭터 목록 불러오기</button>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <select class="form-select" id="characterList" disabled>
                        <option value="null" selected>API Key를 등록해주세요.</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-orange" id="registerButton" type="submit" disabled>회원가입</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>